<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="G" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Gallia" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Gallia,</orth> 1) the Latin name of Wales: <bibl n="shak. wiv 3.1.99" default="NO" valid="yes">Wiv. III, 1, 99</bibl>. 2) of Gaul: <bibl n="shak. h5 1.2.216" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 I, 2, 216</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 1h6 4.7.48" default="NO" valid="yes">H6A IV, 7, 48</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. 3h6 5.3.8" default="NO" valid="yes">H6C V, 3, 8</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 1.6.201" default="NO" valid="yes">Cymb. I, 6, 201</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 2.4.18" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 4, 18</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.5.24" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 5, 24</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 3.7.4" default="NO" valid="yes">III, 7, 4</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.2.333" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 2, 333</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. cym 4.3.24" default="NO" valid="yes">IV, 3, 24</bibl>. <cit><quote>in the G. wars,</quote> <bibl n="shak. h5 5.1.94" default="NO" valid="yes">H5 V, 1, 94</bibl></cit> (Pistol's speech).
